 An applet for the KDE panel containing a pair of eyes that follow your mouse
 around the screen.
 .
 This package is part of KDE3, and a component of the KDE toys module.
 See the 'kde-kde3' and 'kdetoys-kde3' packages for more information.

Package: fifteenapplet-kde3
Architecture: any
Section: kde
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: kicker-kde3
Description: fifteen pieces puzzle for KDE3
 An applet for the KDE panel that lets you play the Fifteen Pieces
 sliding block puzzle. You have to order 15 pieces in a 4x4 square by
 moving them around.
 .
 This package is part of KDE3, and a component of the KDE toys module.
 See the 'kde-kde3' and 'kdetoys-kde3' packages for more information.

