Package: kodo-kde3
Architecture: any
Section: games
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Suggests: khelpcenter-kde3
Conflicts: task-kdetoys-kde3
Replaces: kdetoysv (<< 4:3.0.1-0), task-kdetoys-kde3
Description: mouse odometer for KDE3
 KOdometer measures your desktop mileage. It tracks the movement of your mouse
 pointer across your desktop and renders it in inches/feet/miles! It can
 do cm/metres/km too. Its most exciting feature is the tripometer.
 .
 This package is part of KDE3, and a component of the KDE toys module.
 See the 'kde-kde3' and 'kdetoys-kde3' packages for more information.

Package: kteatime-kde3
Architecture: any
Section: kde
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, kicker-kde3
Suggests: khelpcenter-kde3
Conflicts: task-kdetoys-kde3
Replaces: kdetoys-kde3 (<< 4:3.0.1-0), task-kdetoys-kde3
Description: KDE3 utility for making a fine cup of tea
 KTeaTime is a handy timer for steeping tea. No longer will you have to
 guess at how long it takes for your tea to be ready. Simply select the
 type of tea you have, and it will alert you when the tea is ready to
 drink.
 .
 KTeaTime sits in the KDE3 system tray.
 .
 Please note that KTeaTime is written explicitly for KDE3. If you are
 using a non-KDE window manager or desktop environment then it is quite
 possible that KTeaTime will not work on your system.
 .
 This package is part of KDE3, and a component of the KDE toys module.
 See the 'kde-kde3' and 'kdetoys-kde3' packages for more information.

